#                fired with explicit verdict, repo-invariant fact, BARRIER
#                / OBSTRUCTION_DOCUMENTED with named obstruction, or
#                methodology-spec with concrete numbers
#   - SKIP if  : pure data dump (_index.json / _registry.json / _papers.json
#                / cross_matrix_112x10.json), already cited via sibling
#                shard (n6arch-ai-efficiency-rollup / cross-paper-rollup
#                / structural-rollup), or pure scaffold (compute/cognitive
#                stub .md without falsifiable n6 claim)
#
# Honesty preservation:
#   - All sourced files prefixed with date 2026-04-25 are research-only,
#     "no claim", "0/7 millennium" -- those flags reproduced verbatim.
#   - moonshine-barrier-honest-report-2026-04-15 v2 PARTIAL promotion
#     (σ−τ=8 ⟺ n=6 enumeration over n∈[2,10⁴]) recorded with PARTIAL,
#     NOT promoted to PASS.
#   - All BT-544/541/542/543 candidates: candidate generation, NO
#     RH/P=NP/NS/YM/Poincaré claim.
#
# Grade policy (per shard task):
#   [10*PASS_LITERATURE]  paper-grade with 3-paths or external lit
#   [10*]                 cycle-witness PASS / unconditional integrated paper
#   [10*PARTIAL]          honest-report partial promotion (Mk.IV B candidate)
#   [10*BARRIER]          named BARRIER with mainstream lineage
#   [9*OBSTRUCTION]       OBSTRUCTION_DOCUMENTED with named obstruction
#   [9*CANDIDATE]         candidate generation, no claim
#   [9]                   conditional / NEAR / draft
#   [8]                   spec / plan / methodology document, single source
#   [7]                   uncategorized observation, single source
#
# Dedup audit done against:
#   - atlas.n6 main + atlas.append.*.n6 (510 cited paths)
#   - sibling 2026-04-27 shards (ai-efficiency / cross-paper /
