@R N6ARCH-DEEP-MC-V3-3METRIC = MC v3 三重 metric — A: 12 const greedy z=2.674; B: weighted 944.75 z=1.715; C: stratified Stouffer 0/5 z>2 :: methodology [9]
  => "Source: 1599 valid nodes / 254 unique targets / A·B 2000 trials, C 500/stratum, seed=42."
  => "Metric A (greedy set cover): n=6 needs 12 constants; random mean 18.24; z=2.674 in conservation direction. Coverage 33/254 = 13.0% at all (30/50/70%) thresholds."
  => "Metric B (complexity-weighted): L0=1.0, L1=0.5, L2=0.25; n=6 score 944.75; z=1.715."
  => "Metric C (stratified): 5 strata (L6 macro, L-2~L0 particles, L5 matter/bio, L3-L4 mol/gen, L1-L2 atom/bond); none of the 5 has z>2; Stouffer-combined z absent in source — methodology gap acknowledged."
  |> docs/mc-methodology-v3-report.md
  |> experiments/mc_methodology_v3.hexa

@R N6ARCH-DEEP-MC-V93-DOMAIN = MC v9.3 domain breakdown — 10 domains all z>=3 with materials z=3.4e11 anomaly, gen/mol-bio z=1e10 weakest :: methodology [8]
