  => "Honesty caveat: σ_random=0.00 across 8/10 rows is a numerical artefact, not signal. Treat as a flagged-for-revision report rather than confirmed strength."
  => "Top: 소재/재료 z=3.4e11 (n=20.1% hit on 169 nodes); bottom: 유전/분자생물 z=1e10 (1/51 = 2.0% hit)."
  |> docs/mc-v93-domain-breakdown.md
  |> experiments/mc_v93_by_domain.hexa

